var inputType = 'text';

// Function to remove a filter line
$('.jsRemoveFilterLine').on("click", function(){
if($('.jsFilterLine').length == 2){
$(this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterLine').find('.jsRemoveFilterLine').remove();
}
$(this).parent().remove();
});

// Function to add a filter line
$('.jsAddFilterLine').on("click", function(){
var columnInfos = '';
var defaultOperators = '';

jQuery.each(filterFormOptions, function(key){
columnInfos = columnInfos+'<option label="' + filterFormOptions[key].label + '" value="' + key + '">' + filterFormOptions[key].label + '</option>';
});

jQuery.each(filterFormOptions["id"].operators, function(key, value){
defaultOperators = defaultOperators+'<option label="' + value + '" value="' + key + '">' + value + '</option>';
});

var filterLineTemplate = '<dd class="jsFilterLine">\
<div class="jsFilterColumn">\
<select id="filter-'+ nbFilterSelect +'-column" name="filter['+ nbFilterSelect +'][column]">\
'+ columnInfos +'</select>\
</div>\
<div class="jsFilterOperator">\
<select id="filter-'+ nbFilterSelect +'-operator" name="filter['+ nbFilterSelect +'][operator]">\
'+ defaultOperators +'</select>\
</div>\
<div class="jsFilterValue">\
<input id="filter-'+ nbFilterSelect +'-value" type="'+ inputType +'" value="" name="filter['+ nbFilterSelect +'][value]">\
</div>\
<a class="btn btn-danger btn-xs jsRemoveFilterLine" href="#">X</a>\
</dd>';

if($('.jsFilterLine').length < 2){
$(this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterLine').append('<a class="btn btn-danger btn-xs jsRemoveFilterLine" href="#">X</a>');
}

$(this).parent().parent().prepend(filterLineTemplate);
nbFilterSelect = nbFilterSelect + 1;
});

// Select the input type and fill in the second "select"
$('.jsFilterColumn select').on("change", function(){
var selectId = $(this).attr('id');
if (selectId.match(/^[a-z\-]+[0-9]+\-column$/)){
filterOperators($(this));
}
});


function filterOperators(element){
// Fill in the second "select"
var $this = element;
var inputId;
var selectToReplace = '';
var inputOptions = '';
var radios = '';

$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterOperator').find('select').find('option').replaceWith('');

jQuery.each(filterFormOptions[$($this).val()].operators, function(key, value){
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterOperator').find('select').append('<option label="' + value + '" value="' + key + '">' + value + '</option>');
});
inputType = filterFormOptions[$($this).val()].inputType;
inputId = $($this).attr('name').substr(7,1);

//Input type selection
switch(inputType){
case "select" : jQuery.each(filterFormOptions[$($this).val()].inputOptions, function(key, value){
inputOptions = inputOptions + '<option label="' + value + '" value="' + key + '">' + value + '</option>';
});

if ($($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('a.ui-multiselect') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('select'))
{
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').replaceWith('<div class="jsFilterValue">\
<select id="filter-'+ inputId +'-value" name="filter['+ inputId +'][value]">'+ inputOptions +'</select>\
</div>');
}

inputType='text';
break;

case "radio" :jQuery.each(filterFormOptions[$($this).val()].inputOptions, function(key, value){
radios = radios + '<input type="radio" name="filter['+ key +'][value]" value="'+ value +'"/>';
});

if ($($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('a.ui-multiselect') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('select'))
{
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').replaceWith('<div class="jsFilterValue">\
'+ radios +'\
</div>');
}

inputType='text';
break;

case "multiselect" :jQuery.each(filterFormOptions[$($this).val()].inputOptions, function(key, value){
inputOptions = inputOptions + '<option label="' + value + '" value="' + key + '">' + value + '</option>';
});

if ($($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('a.ui-multiselect') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('select'))
{
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').replaceWith('<div class="jsFilterValue">\
<select id="filter-'+ inputId +'-value" multiple="multiple" name="filter['+ inputId +'][value][]">' + inputOptions + '</select>\
</div>');
}

$('select[multiple=multiple]').multiselect();
inputType='text';
break;

case "datetime" :
case "date" : if ($($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('a.ui-multiselect') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('select'))
{
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').replaceWith('<div class="jsFilterValue">\
<input id="filter-'+ inputId +'-value" type="text" value="" name="filter['+ inputId +'][value]"/>\
</div>');
}

if (inputType == "date") {$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input').removeClass(); $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input').datepicker({ dateFormat: 'yy-mm-dd' });}
else {$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input').removeClass(); $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input').datetimepicker({showSecond: true, dateFormat: 'yy-mm-dd', timeFormat: 'hh:mm:ss'});}

inputType='text';
break;

default : if ($($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('a.ui-multiselect') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('input') || $($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').find('select'))
{
$($this).parent().siblings('.jsFilterValue').replaceWith('<div class="jsFilterValue">\
<input id="filter-'+ inputId +'-value" type="text" value="" name="filter['+ inputId +'][value]"/>\
</div>');
}
break;
}
}
});
